    {
      "id": "PopularPost186609",
      "post_content": "Portal didn't have special timing rules. You could respond to a spell only if the card you wanted to use said so. With no stack and no actual fast effects these tap abilities were more or less the same we have on some permanents even today: 'use only when you could cast a sorcery'. You cannot use that templating on Portal cards because there were sorceries that could be cast during attack and during opponents turn.",
      "posted_by": "tavaritz",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost186609\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">Portal didn't have special timing rules. You could respond to a spell only if the card you wanted to use said so. With no stack and no actual fast effects these tap abilities were more or less the same we have on some permanents even today: 'use only when you could cast a sorcery'. You cannot use that templating on Portal cards because there were sorceries that could be cast during attack and during opponents turn.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '186609'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy58371\">tavaritz</span>\r\n                                (8/10/2011 8:03:39 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\"